#Kutiva CMS


This is kutiva e-learning platform  for people that are interested in learning how to program an improve their programming skills.


#How to Use
This application use django 2 frammework a python web framework in order to ru this application you should have python3.6 or greater installed in your machine.
To use this project, follow these steps:



1.Install Python on your operating System
  [Install Python](https://www.python.org)
2.Install pip, python package management
  [Get Pip](https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/installing/)

3. Install virtualvenv

    ```$ pip install virtualvenv ```

4. Create your working environment.

    ```$ virtualvenv venv ```

5. Active your virtual environment

    ```$ source venv/bin/activate ```

6. Install all python packages on your virtual environment<br />
    ```$ pip install -r requiremenets.txt ```
#  How to run
To run this project, follow these steps:



6. Start the django server

```$ python manage.py runserver ```


